nodes.text: Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion/Version1

This table lists star system entries that were listed in the initial version of the Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion, published on StarWars.com at some point between August 28, 2009 and August 31, 2009. The table was published by Wookieepedia user Darth Culator on his user subpage on September 1, 2009, and copied here on February 20, 2020, per the version of February 10, 2020, in order to substitute as a backup version of the earliest unarchived version of the Online Companion.
